# Linux Installation (Raspberry Pi Zero 2 W)

Run the following command before installing the Python package requirements:

    ```bash
    sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install -y \
        python3-pip \
        build-essential \
        cmake \
        pkg-config \
        libx11-dev \
        libatlas-base-dev \
        libgtk-3-dev \
        libboost-python-dev \
        python3-numpy \
        python3-picamera2 \
        libcblas-dev \
        libhdf5-dev \
        libhdf5-serial-dev \
        libjasper-dev \
        libqtgui4 \
        libqt4-test \
        libgstreamer1.0-0
    